

SAKTO

   This word is a shortening of the Filipino word eksakto, which is from
   the Spanish exacto.

   eksaktong kita
   fixed income

   Saktong-sakto…
   Very exact
   = Just right

   This could also be translated as “right when…” or “right as.”

   Saktong pagkakita ko sa kanila…
   Right when I saw them…

   Another spelling variation: iksakto
